    {
      "name": "The Indigo Flame",
      "type": "feature",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>PCs who approach the central tree can make a Knowledge Roll to try to identify the magic that consumed this environment. </p><ul><li><p><strong>On a success:</strong> They learn three of the below details. On a success with Fear, they learn two. </p></li><li><p><strong>On a failure:</strong> They can mark a Stress to learn one and gain advantage on the next action roll to investigate this environment. </p></li><li><p><strong>Details:</strong> This is a result of Fallen magic. The corruption is spread through the ashen moss. It can be cleansed only by a ritual of nature magic with a Progress Countdown (8).</p></li></ul><section id=\"secret-SkDRzA8454MaIFU3\" class=\"secret\"><p><em>What Fallen cult corrupted these woods? What have they already done with the cursed wood and sap from this tree?</em></p></section>",
